{"word":"ἄντομος","slug":"ἄντομος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n10760\" key=\"a)/ntomos\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ἄντομος</orth>, <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">ὁ</gen>, dialectic form of <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἀνάτομος,</foreign> <sense id=\"n10760.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">stake</tr_> or <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">pale,</tr_> cf. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἄντομοι· σκόλοπες</foreign> (<placeName TEIform=\"placeName\">Sicel</placeName>), <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hsch.\">Hsch.</a></author> </bibl>: hence collectively, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">paling, boundary-fence,</tr_> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Tab.Heracl.\">Tab.Heracl.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.15</biblScope></bibl>, al.; also, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">road adjoining such a fence,</tr_> ib.<bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.13</biblScope></bibl>, al.</sense> </entryFree>"}]}